<div class="details theme-blue" data-id="2620151" data-title="Local initiative raising money to help create &#39;Period Packs&#39;" data-tag="96994">
<h1 class="title details-title">Local initiative raising money to help create 'Period Packs'</h1>
    <div class="details-intro">Changing the Flow wants to help people who cannot afford to buy pads and tampons</div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-7 details-byline">
                    <time datetime="2020-08-07T10:30:00.0000000Z">Aug 7, 2020 6:30 AM</time>
                          By:     <span id="author">Aastha Shetty</span>


                
            </div>
